tafsir[59]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,"Haa, Miim. Yewtere fii sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka simoore Al baqarah."
  44,2,"Allah woondirii Deftere …ìannginnde laawol peewal ngol."
  44,3,"Men jippinirii Alqur'aana, e jemma laylatul qadiri: jemma hebbiniraa…óo barki, Men siforii wonde jertiniroo…ìe ndee Alqur'aanaare."
  44,4,"Ko e nder on jemma, woni ko kala fiyaaku √±e√±aa…óo, humondir…óo e arsike maa lajal ekn, woni ko Allah siinata e nden hitaande."
  44,5,"Me…óen senndira kala fiyaaku √±e√±aa…óo immorde ka Amen. Men siforii wonde imminoo…ìe Nulaa…ìe."
  44,6,"Me…óen imminira Nulaa…ìe …ìen, yurmeende Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo, yurmegol Nulaa…ìe e mun …ìen. Pellet, Kanko Allah, ko O Nanoowo haalaaji jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Anndu…óo kuu…óe e annuyeeji ma…ì…ìe …óin. Hunnde e …óin suu…óaaki Mo."
  44,7,"Jey…óo kadi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si wonii ko on yananaa…ìe …óum, haray gom…óinee Nulaa…ìe Am …ìen."
  44,8,"Rewetee…óo e goonga woo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Himo wuurna, Himo wara, wuurnoowo wara alaa, si wana Kanko. Jey…óo on Jeyi baabiraa…ìe mon adinoo…ìe …ìen."
  44,9,"∆Åee sirkoo…ìe yananaaka e …óum. Si ko woni, hi…ìe sikkitii…ói …óum, …ìe woni e fijugol e meere."
  44,10,"Habbitoyo Nulaa…óo, lepte yim…ìe maa …ìadii…óe hewtu…óe, √±alnde kammu ngun ardata e curki fee√±ayngu e gite ma…ì…ìe, hakkee ko …ìe sattina heege muusnge."
  44,11,"Hara curki kin hino sudda yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe wi'anee ontuma: ko lepte muusu…óe woni ko he…ìi on."
  44,12,"∆Åe wona e tororgol Joomi ma…ì…ìe wi'ugol: Joomi amen, huncan men …óee lepte, haray ko men gom…óinoo…ìe ma e Nulaa…óo Maa on, si A huncanii men …óe."
  44,13,"Ko honno …ìe waajitorta, …ìe tuubana Joomi ma…ì…ìe, hara le Nulaa…óo ariino …ìe, …ìannginani …ìe Nulal ngal, …ìe anndi le ko o goongu…óo hoolnii…óo?"
  44,14,"Refti …ìe …óuurnii e goongingol mo ngol, …ìe wi'i mo: ko go…ó…óo goo woni e anndinnde mo, o wonah Nulaa…óo, haa …ìe wi'oyi: ko o haangaa…óo."
  44,15,"Tuma Men huncani on lepte …óen yeru see…óa; pellet, on ruttitoto e keeferaaku e fennugol mon ngol."
  44,16,"Habbito …ìe yo Nulaa…óo, haa √ëalnde Men nanngiroyta yim…ìe maa yeddu…ìe …ìen, wippannde manwde nden Badri, haray pellet, ko Men yottoytoo…ìe e ko …ìe yeddiri kon Allah, …ìe fenni Nulaa…óo Makko on."
  44,17,"Gom…óii Men jerribinoke ado ma…ì…ìe, yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, Nulaa…óo Allah teddu…óo, ari e ma…ì…ìe, himo nodda …ìe e wootin…óingol rewa Allah: on woni Muusaa (yo o his)."
  44,18,"Muusaa maakani Fir'awna e yim…ìe mun …ìen: accidee lam e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, tawde ko …ìe jeyaa…ìe Allah. Haqqe alanaa on e maccin…óingol …ìe. Awa min wonannde on, ko mi Nulaa…óo Allah e mon, hoolnii…óo e ko Allah nuli lam yottingol kon, mi …óuytataa mi …ìeydataa e mun."
  44,19,"E wonde wata townitanor Allah, tertagol rewude Mo, townitanoo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, tawde min on, mi addanay on hujja …ìanngu…óo."
  44,20,"Min kadi non, mi moolorii Jey…óo lam On Jeyi on, nde warirtonmi kaa∆¥e."
  44,21,"Si on gom…óinaa ko mi addi kon, haray wo…ó…óitee lam, hara on hewtiraali lam bone."
  44,22,"Annabi Muusaa noddiri Joomi mun, wonnde …ìee yim…ìe Fir'awna …óoo e dental mun …óoo, ko bom…ìe hanndu…ìe e yaccinaneede lepte."
  44,23,"Allah yamiri Muusaa yaadugol e yim…ìe makko …ìen jemma, O humpiti mo, wonnde Fir'awna e yim…ìe non, ko jokkitoo…ìe mo."
  44,24,"Allah yamiri mo lummbidugol e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen ka maayo, O acca ngo ko dee∆¥a, tawde Fir'awna e konu mun ngun, kalkirete yooleteede ka maaya."
  44,25,"∆äuu…óii ko Fir'awna e yim…ìe mun acci …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, immorde e gese e …ìulli ilooji."
  44,26,"∆Åe acci kadi remuruujo e ko…óan…óe labaa…óe."
  44,27,"E ko…ìe acci caggal mum en e nguurndam …ìe wonunoo neeminireede."
  44,28,"Ko wano siforano…óon non, fe∆¥∆¥irnoo e ma…ì…ìe. Men ronini …óin neemaaji ma…ì…ìe, yim…ìe goo, …ìen woni …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen."
  44,29,"Kammu ngun wullaali yoolagol Fir'awna e yim…ìe mun …ìen, wanaa leydi ndin, …ìe wonaali kadi mu√±√±orantee…ìe no …ìe tuubira."
  44,30,"Gom…óii Men da…óndii …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìn e lepte hoynooje, tawde Fi'awna e yim…ìe mun …ìen, laatino waroo…ìe …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe wor…ìe, …ìe acca rew…ìe …ìen."
  44,31,"Men da…óndi mo e lepte Fir'awna …óen, tawde o wonuno mawnintinii…óo fantini e yawitagol yamaruyee e diina Allah kan."
  44,32,"Gom…óii Men su…ìorike …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen e dow anndal Amen, e hoore winndere jamaanu ma…ì…ìe, tawde …ìe …óuu…óirano Annabaa…ìe."
  44,33,"Men okki …ìe hujjaaji …ói Men semmbiniri Muusaa, …ói neema fee√±irani …ìe e mun, wano manna e colli ju…óaa…ói."
  44,34,"∆Åee sirkoo…ìe fennoo…ìe no wi'a e yeddugol ummital:"
  44,35,"Ndee maayde wonaali, si wanaa aranere nden tun, men wonaali kadi immintinoytee…ìe …ìaawo mun."
  44,36,"Awa Muhammadu, an e jokku…ìe ma …ìen, artiree baabiraa…ìe amen maaynoo…ìe …ìen, si wonii ko e goonga won…óon, wonnde Allah immintinay maay…ìe …ìen, fii √±aaweede yo…ìitee."
  44,37,"Kere ko …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennu…ìe ma an Nulaa…óo, …ìuri cemmbe e neema, kaa ko yim…ìe ""Tubba'in"" …ìen e …ìeya adinoo…ìe …ìe, wano 'Adi'en e Samuuda'en, Men halkuno …ìen fow, tawde ko …ìe laatina bom…ìe."
  44,38,"Me tagiraali kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, fijoo…ìe e …óum."
  44,39,"Men tagiraali kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, si wanaa fii √±e√±∆¥al faandaangal. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e sirkoo…ìe …ìen, …ìe anndaa …óum."
  44,40,"Pellet, ko √ëalnde Darngal, woni ko Allah saatini senndindirgol hakkunde jeyaa…ìe …ìen, …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe, tuma …ìe moo…ìindiraa."
  44,41,"√ëalnde nde gi…óo woo nafoytaa gi…óo mun ; …ìe wonaali kadi da…óoo…ìe lepte Allah …óen, tawde Laamu ngun nden √ëalnde, ko Allah woodani, wanaa go…ó…óo e nodditoraynoo…ìe ngu."
  44,42,"Si wanaa ne…ó…óo mo Allah yurmaa woo, on …óon nafitoroy golle makko mo∆¥∆¥e …óen. Pellet, Allah ko Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake, Hinnotoo…óo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  44,43,"Pellet, leggal Zaqquumi ngal Allah fu…óini ngal ka asli Yiite,"
  44,44,"Ko ngal woni √±aamdu …óuu…óu…ìe bakkaatu …ìen, woni heefero o na nyaama e …ìesnooje makki co…ì…óe …óe."
  44,45,"Nde …ìesnaande na nanndi e nebban …ìale nde taayinaa, hara hino fata e deedi ma…ì…ìe …óin, hakkee ko wuli."
  44,46,"Wano ndiyam wul…óam jaw nguli fatirta."
  44,47,"Ayninaay…ìe Yiite ngen wi'anee: nanngee mo poo…óiron doole, haa ka hakkunde Jahiimi."
  44,48,"Refti yuppon ka hoore makko, ndiyam fasnaa…óam …óam, hara o seertataa e lepte …óen."
  44,49,"O wi'anee ontuma: awa mee…óu non lepte muusu…óe …óen ! An sikkunoo…óo ko a foolu…óo mo dartetaake, teddu…óo hakkunde yim…ìe mun."
  44,50,"Awa ko …óee lepte woni ko sikkitino…óon si laatotono √ëalnde Darngal sikke iwii e mon caggal On fellitii hannde."
  44,51,"Pellet, hulir…ìe Joomi mun …ìen …óoftagol Mo ha…óitoo e ha…óaa…ói Makko, …ìen wonii e weerde hoolniinde e kala bone."
  44,52,"E nder gese e …ìulli ilay…ói."
  44,53,"Hi…ìe …ìoornoo ka Aljanna ton, comci …óaatu…ói e tekku…ói, hara hi…ìe fewtondiri, …ìe runtandirtaa."
  44,54,"Ko wano Men teddiniri …ìe non …óin jantaa…ói, Men resiniri …ìe kadi ka Aljanna, rew…ìe yaaju…ìe gite, tii…óu…ìe …ìaleeri gite."
  44,55,"Hi…ìe golloo…ìe ton …ìen, fii addangol …ìe kala muuyantee…ói …ói …ìe faaletee, hara ko …ìe hoolii…ìe e anngal ta∆¥ondirgol …ói maa lorra majji."
  44,56,"Ko …ìe duumotoo…ìe ton, …ìe mee…óataa ton maayde woo, si wanaa maayde aranere nden aduna, Joomi ma…ì…ìe da…ónda …ìe lepte Yiite ngen."
  44,57,"∆äum ko dokkal e mo∆¥∆¥ere immorde ka Joomi maa. Haray ko jantaa koo, e naadeede …ìen Aljanna, da…ónda …ìe Yiite, ko …óum woni maloore mawnde nden, nde sugu mun alaa."
  44,58,"Ko Men newinirani ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinirgol nde e …óemngal maa, aarabu ngal, an Nulaa…óo, ko no …ìe waajitora."
  44,59,"Habbito faabo maa ngon e halkeede …ìe nden. Kam…ìe ko …ìe habbitii…ìe maayde maa."
